== 製作 ==

=== 選角 ===
2006年12月19日，導演[[羅伯·殭屍|羅伯·殭屍]]對《{{link-en|Bloody Disgusting|Bloody Disgusting}}》宣布，{{link-en|狄哥·菲爾屈|Daeg Faerch}}將飾演十歲時的{{le|麥克·邁爾斯 (月光光心慌慌)|Michael Myers (Halloween)|麥克·邁爾斯}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/36/16536.php|title=Daeg Faerch to Play a Young Michael Myers in the Next Halloween Movie|publisher=Movieweb.net|date=2006-12-19|accessdate=2007-06-13|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070707103123/http://www.movieweb.com/news/36/16536.php|archivedate=2007-07-07}}</ref>。同年12月22日，[[麥坎·邁道爾|麥坎·邁道爾]]確認出演{{link-en|山繆·魯米斯|Samuel Loomis|山姆·魯米斯醫生}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://profile.myspace.com/28735418|publisher=MySpace|title=Rob Zombie's MySpace|date=2006-12-22|accessdate=2007-04-09|archive-date=2012-07-12|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120712193712/http://profile.myspace.com/28735418|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。24日，殭屍表示，曾經拒絕參演殭屍執導的電影《[[獵殺猛鬼公路|獵殺猛鬼公路]]》的演員{{link-en|泰勒·曼恩|Tyler Mane}}，將詮釋成年的麥克·邁爾斯<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/7875|title=Michael Myers cast in Rob Zombie's 'Halloween'|publisher=Bloody-Disgusting|date=2006-11-24|accessdate=2008-10-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081025174227/http://www.bloody-disgusting.com/news/7875|archivedate=2008-10-25}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《惡靈07 月光光心慌慌》於2007年8月31日在北美的3,472家劇院同步上映<ref name="mainpage">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=halloween07.htm|title=Main Page Summary|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2008-08-17|archive-date=2019-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190121125754/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=halloween07.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其同步上映的劇院數超越[[月光光心慌慌系列電影|月光光心慌慌系列電影]]中的任何一部<ref name="compare">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=halloween.htm|title=''Halloween'' film series comparison chart|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-03-03|archive-date=2015-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151117020118/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/franchises/chart/?id=halloween.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
電影收穫了普遍影評人的差評。[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的110篇專業影評文章中，僅有28篇給予該片「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為25%，[[加權平均數|平均得分]]4.1分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1179254-halloween/|title=Halloween|publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2011-08-18|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201190350/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1179254-halloween|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而基於另一影評匯總網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的18篇評論文章，其中4篇予以好評，6篇差評，8篇褒貶不一，平均分為47（滿分100）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/halloween2007|title=Halloween (2007): Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2007-09-09|archive-date=2010-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100515200814/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/halloween2007|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「B-」並指出，62%的觀眾是男性，57%為25歲或以上<ref>{{cite journal|author=Gregg Kilday|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idUSN3019801620070905|title='Watchmen' takes box office lead|journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2007-09-05|accessdate=2009-03-08|archive-date=2009-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090504015445/http://www.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idUSN3019801620070905|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
首映當天，《惡靈07 月光光心慌慌》票房達到10,896,610美元<ref name="DBO">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=halloween07.htm|title=Daily Box Office Totals|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-03-03|archive-date=2018-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181021065910/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=daily&id=halloween07.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，從9月1日至2日，電影分別收入8,554,661及6,911,096美元，在為期3天的首映週末總計26,362,367美元。而在[[勞動節|勞動節]]中額外收穫4,229,392美元，使該週最終票房為30,591,759美元<ref name="DBO"/>，位居冠軍<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=35a&p=.htm|title=August 31–September 3, 2007|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-03-03|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629081321/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=35a&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在首映週末後的第一個星期五，電影的票房下滑了71.6%，共收入3,093,679美元<ref name="DBO"/>，第二個週末總計僅9,513,770美元，較上週下降63.9%，但仍位居當週亞軍，僅次《[[決鬥猶馬鎮|決鬥猶馬鎮]]》<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=36&p=.htm|title=September 7–9, 2007|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-03-03|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629080851/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=36&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《惡靈07 月光光心慌慌》直到第三個週末仍保持在前十名；獲得4,867,522美元排名第六<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=37&p=.htm|title=September 14–16, 2007|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-03-03|archive-date=2018-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629082124/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=37&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影於次週即跌到第12名，票房2,189,266美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=38&p=.htm|title=September 21–23, 2007|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-03-03|archive-date=2018-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181113015735/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2007&wknd=38&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《惡靈07 月光光心慌慌》在接下來的週末皆無法回歸至前十名的地位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekend&id=halloween07.htm|title=Weekend rankings for 2007|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2009-03-03|archive-date=2009-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090225035559/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekend&id=halloween07.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於電影在首週末共收穫3,050萬美元，打破了勞動節週末的票房紀錄，超越2005年《[[玩命快遞2|玩命快遞2]]》所締造的成績（2,010萬美元）<ref>{{cite news|author=Gregg Kilday|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/09/05/AR2007090500182_pf.html|title="Halloween" pulls neat trick at box office|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2007-09-05|accessdate=2008-08-17|archive-date=2017-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313104034/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/09/05/AR2007090500182_pf.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，截止至今，仍然保持著此地位<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/laborday.htm?page=LABDAY&p=.htm|title=Labor Day Record|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2008-08-17|archive-date=2016-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618175506/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/alltime/weekends/laborday.htm?page=LABDAY&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《惡靈07 月光光心慌慌》同時也是2007年票房第八高的[[美国电影分级制度|R級電影]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/mpaarating.htm?rating=R&yr=2007&p=.htm|title=R-rated 2007 films|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2008-08-17|archive-date=2018-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180527231042/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/mpaarating.htm?rating=R&yr=2007&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，且在年度電影票房中位居第44名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2007&p=.htm|title=2007 Domestic Grosses|publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|accessdate=2008-08-17|archive-date=2019-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920151322/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/yearly/chart/?yr=2007&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

